  "id": "MGASA-2014-0075",
  "summary": "Updated libpng and libpng12 packages fix security vulnerability",
  "details": "The png_do_expand_palette function in libpng before 1.6.8 allows remote\nattackers to cause a denial of service (NULL pointer dereference and\napplication crash) via a PLTE chunk of zero bytes or a NULL palette, related\nto pngrtran.c and pngset.c (CVE-2013-6954).\n",
